name: The monoliths #6
description: The sixth piece in the monoliths series was sent to @sizenewxyz on the 20th of September 2021 in the second year of the pandemic. This is a Monday which means a lot of phone calls. Monday is for the calls we knew we had to make and Friday is for the calls we knew we had to make on Monday but we never called and now it is Friday afternoon. I think they must teach this in business school.
